So split it into 2 or rephrase it, ie  “will my boyf visit me?” & “will his visit be today?”

or “is today a day my boyf will visit me?” 

Honestly HOW you ask something can make all the difference!

Pendulum work can be very useful, as long as you only ask for yourself or with permission from another, and only ask one question at a time (be careful not to ask two in one like “is my boyf gonna visit me today” - it is 2 questions “the visit” and “today” -it will only answer 1!

Maybe why I’ve felt so conflicted about the whole thing because “technically” we aren’t TFs YET so I’ve accidentally not be truthful, on a technicality. Oops. 🙊
